     <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
			   <div class="block">
			   <img src="img/1.png">
				  <h1><b>Vetting</b> Committee</h1>
				   <p>Volunteers play a big role in reviewing all loan applications made to us.<br><br>
				   Volunteers have the chance to learn about the stories of various impact makers across industries and how they are making a difference to their communities.</p></div>
          </div>
           <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
			   <div class="block">
	           <img src="img/2.png">
	           <h1><b>Storyteller</b> Committee</h1>
				   <p>Volunteers have the opportunity to speak to actual loan applicants to hear their stories by “adopting” a loan.<br><br>The purpose? To share and tell the world how much of a difference this individual or organisation and their loan would make to their communities - whether through an article,video or any othermethods.</p>
			   </div>
		 </div>
		   <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
			   <div class="block">
	           <img src="img/3.png">
	            <h1><b>Engagement</b> Committee</h1>
				   <p>Volunteers play the two fold role of liaising with our partners in local communities and work on donor &amp; volunteerengagement.<br><br>Volunteers would work with our local partners on improving the experience and success of borrowers. They would also work on events and other volunteer engagement initiatives.</p>
              </div>
	      </div>
	 </div>
